advisories.title: Prototype Pollution in hoek
hoek subject to prototype pollution via the clone function.
advisories.description: hoek versions prior to 8.5.1, and 9.x prior to 9.0.3 are vulnerable to prototype pollution in the clone function. If an object with the __proto__ key is passed to clone() the key is converted to a prototype. This issue has been patched in version 9.0.3, and backported to 8.5.1.
